<!--
  Power Panel - Moonraker power device control

  Features (planned):
  - List all configured power devices
  - On/Off/Toggle controls for each device
  - Status indicators (on/off/locked)
  - Lock critical devices during print
  - Quick access from home screen

  Moonraker API:
  - GET /machine/device_power/devices
  - GET /machine/device_power/device?device=<name>
  - POST /machine/device_power/device (action: on/off/toggle)

  Status: STUB - Coming Soon
  See: docs/FEATURE_STATUS.md for implementation progress
-->
